verbose_text: FICZ has a high affinity to the aryl hydrocarbon receptor (AhR) and activates AhR response genes, including cyclooxygenase-2 (Cox2), a melanoma prognostic marker gene [XREF_BIBR], and cytochrome P4501A1, which increases ROS accumulation [XREF_BIBR].
